                                        2161,
                                        2301,
                                        2805
                                    ],
                                    "type": "text",
                                    "content": " respectively. Since the capacitance also depends on temperature, after placing the samples between two plates, simultaneous measurements of the temperature inside the box and capacitance were carried out. The temperature data were acquired using a Pico TC- 08 Data Logger. The system's capacitance in the first approximation can be estimated by fitting the impedance data to an equivalent circuit."
